   &UR; U.S. `COVERED UP' SCIENTISTS' WARNINGS ON GM FOODS &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   LONDON _ British Prime Minister Tony Blair's fresh skepticism
about GM (genetically-modified) foods was bolstered Monday by
claims that the U.S. government has covered up the safety fears of
its own scientists. &QL;
</P>
<P>
   By Jack O'Sullivan, The Independent of London &QL;
