<P>
   CHINA-CALIF (San Francisco) _ China's increasingly tense
relations with Taiwan reared its head in California's U.S. Senate
race as Republican hopeful Tom Campbell called on rival Sen. Dianne
Feinstein to rebuff Beijing's tough talk. By ANNIE NAKAO.
