<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-29 14:35 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2056 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u t BC-TRAVEL-DURANGO-BOS &LR;      02-29 1691
