issue of paid reparations for American slavery from the fringes of
black political debate onto the mainstream civil rights agenda, a
group of prominent black academics is looking into a class-action
lawsuit. By Tatsha Robertson. 1000 words.
</P>
<P>
   BIRACIAL-GENERATION (Undated) _ A new generation of young,
biracial people are refusing to be categorized within the slim
confines of black, white, Hispanic, Native American. By Vanessa
Jones. 1350 words. PHOTO
