Delouvrier.
</P>
<P>
   With recipe.
</P>
<P>
   With photo.
</P>
<P>
   VIETNAM-BOOK-REVIEW (Undated) _ Mark Bittman reviews ``Authentic
Vietnamese Cooking'' by Corinne Trang.
</P>
<P>
   With recipe.
