   CLEAR-SFX (Undated) _ In another giant deal that is emblematic
of the increasing consolidation and concentration of media and
entertainment interests, a big broadcast and outdoor advertising
company, Clear Channel Communications Inc., said Tuesday that it
would acquire SFX Entertainment Inc., the largest producer of live
concerts, theater and sports events, for about $3.3 billion in
stock. By Stuart Elliott.
</P>
