SAN FRANCISCO _  WINTER BLAHS  _ You might call this the awkward
season _ it's March, which means that spring is not too far off, at
the same time it's still the dead of winter. Produce bins, by and
large, yield little excitement, so we are challenged to put pizzazz
into our menus. &HT;    Main story, recipes and sidebar. 
 By Karola Saekel  
 c. 1999 The San Francisco Chronicle  
