 &QL; 
SANTA ROSA, Calif. _  &UR; SOURCECHEESE &LR;  _ For Sylvia Tucker,
cheesemaking is a hands-on affair _ literally. Most days, she
hand-mixes curds to make St. George cheese at Joe Matos Cheese Co.,
her parents' farm and business outside Santa Rosa, where 25 to 30
Holsteins graze in mooing distance of a small factory and sales
room.
