<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-29 19:55 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2440 &Cx1f; taf-z
u w BC-SCOTUS-2TAKES(770)-NY     02-29 0801
