<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-29 20:55 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2515 &Cx1f; taf-z
u p BC-ELN-ASSESS-NYT &LR;      02-29 1016
